{"tid":2076963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳副主席坐正 CFO任看守CEO 海洋公園長遠續尋人才覓重生路","createTime":"2020-06-24T02:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T05:06:13.000Z","uid":144018,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cc03db0ad2a871f5d40aab1caec2f685d6892426","tid":2076963,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7QOiLc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7QOiLc.jpg&h=8e943d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1999060633703896/posts/2800493426893942/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1999060633703896%2Fposts%2F2800493426893942%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=4606cd94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1999060633703896/posts/2800493426893942/</a><br />\n<br />\n據悉加入公園董事會逾10年的副主席會「坐正」接任主席一職，而行政總裁則由首席財務總監暨公司秘書接任<br />\n　<br />\n據了解公園於2019年便透過全球招聘物色行政總裁繼任人選，但先後遇上武漢肺炎及財困風波加上公園現時只能支撐營運一年。故此公園決定從現任管理層中擢升以縮短新任行政總裁的適應時間，據知公園傾向由現首席財務總監暨公司秘書接任行政總裁一職，為繼現任行政總裁後第二個首席財務總監出身的行政總裁。但現任行政總裁一直被指缺乏管理主題公園經驗，更指其以管理財務的手法管理公園是引致是次面臨倒閉危機的主因。因此消息稱新任行政總裁只屬看守性質，未來會繼續尋找管理主題樂園的專才出任行政總裁一職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒「坐正」做海洋公園主席 <br />\n揸數CFO或升任看守CEO「睇餸食飯」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/PWE5PKYLY4773UES4Z6UCYAV5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FPWE5PKYLY4773UES4Z6UCYAV5E%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=dc49facf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FPWE5PKYLY4773UES4Z6UCYAV5E%2F&h=986deecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/PWE5PKYLY4773UES4Z6UCYAV5E/</a>"},{"pid":"b6780e78f13a0861e92d56b27745b5c65b29d077","tid":2076963,"uid":144018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T02:48:33.000Z","msg":"Pa